snippet.title: Day 2: ET India Inc. Boardroom
snippet.description: Day 2 has business leaders from the retail sector sharing their survival playbook, deliberating upon models for driving experiential retail and sustainable growth. Speakers for the day include Hari Vasudev of Walmart Labs, Abheek Singhi of Boston Consulting Group, Raghu Krishnananda of Myntra Jabong, Pratik Pota of Jubilant Foodworks, Sangeeta Pendurkar of Aditya Birla Fashion and Retail, Vishak Kumar of Madura Fashion and Lifestyle, Ambareesh Murty of Pepperfry, Abhishek Ganguly of Puma, Devendra Chawla of Spencers Retail and Nitin Chabbra of Ace Turtle, among others.
